  "texts": [
    "Besides the quantitative assessment of the ChatGPT answers, we allowed all participants to submit free text comments for each answer.",
    "In total, the participants submitted 355 free text comments.",
    "The complete list of free text comments can be found in the supplementary information.",
    "We manually assigned all free text comments into three inductive main categories: Lack of detail, answer quality, and comparison to students.",
    "This coding process was performed by three authors of this study, who are faculty members with no industry experience, among consensual coding sessions; final results are therefore unanimous and fully inter-coder-reliable 41."
